structure Bar where
  foobar : Nat
structure Foo where
  x : Bar
example (f : Foo) : Nat × Nat :=
  ⟨f.x.foobar, f.x.f⟩
example (b : Bar) : Nat × Nat :=
  ⟨b.foobar, b.f⟩
